I'm sorry to hear you're experiencing an error with your card. Could you please provide more details about the error message you're seeing? This will help me assist you better.

If your card authorization failed, I recommend contacting your bank to resolve the payment issue. Alternatively, you can try adding a different payment method to your account. If you choose to update your account with a different payment method, don't forget to resubmit your ads! You can also add ad credits as a short-term solution. For more details, you can refer to our Billing Guide here: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide).
how much amount in card for authorization ?

We have a temporary $10 card authorization fee. If you run ads, this amount goes towards your advertising budget; otherwise, if you don't run ads, it will be fully refunded. The payment amount is held for 7 days, and if not captured within this time, Stripe cancels the payment and releases the funds. For more information, you can check our Billing Guide here: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide).
Great! If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask. I'm here to help!
Could you please provide more details about what you're looking for regarding auto insurance? Are you inquiring about an ad, policy, or something else? This will help me assist you better.
I want to run ads for auto insurance, but before that, I would like to ask how auto insurance offers work on your platform. Will I receive leads or not?

Running ads for auto insurance on NewsBreak can help you reach a targeted audience. However, the platform primarily focuses on impressions and clicks rather than direct lead generation. You can use Cost Per Click (CPC) or Cost Per Mille (CPM) pricing models to drive traffic to your landing page where you can capture leads. For more details on advertising costs and strategies, you can refer to our Advertising Cost Guide here: [Advertising Cost Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17959734533005-NewsBreak-Advertising-Cost).
You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
